subproject.description: This project will achieve: (1) Existing systems/policies/standards/ guidelines are enhanced/ new ones are established; (2) institutional and technical capacities on EEL applications developed; (3) consumer awareness on EEL applications improved; (4) EEL initiatives financing assistance program implemented; (5) management and disposal of mercury congaing lamp waste are environmentally acceptable.
subproject.title: Philippine Efficient Lighting
